title: Looking for team
body: Looking for team Bronze 3+ just getting back into this game, Main-mid/Jungle

replies.body:
Hey there! Looks like you may have made your way to the OCE Team Recruitment sub-boards by mistake. If you're looking for players on NA to play with, try the Team Recruitment sub-boards on the North American Boards!

http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/team-recruitment
